development of tuberculosis in patients who tested negative for latent tuberculosis infection prior to initiating therapy.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/150244/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, More', 'Entrectinib, Dacomitinib, Tepotinib, Lapatinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Capmatinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, Encorafenib, Axitinib, More', 1767369485);
